title: Ecologists vs. Vegans & Why There Are No Comments on this Youtube channel
description:
If you want to skip to the answer to the question of why I disabled comments on this youtube channel, click to the 15:08 mark.
If you'd like to see the youtube channel of the fellow who sent in the comment (read aloud in this video), click here for "Sustainable Vegan" by Haruki: https://www.youtube.com/user/kaimotueka/videos
